  <brief_title>Reduced Chemotherapy in Low Risk DLBCL</brief_title>
  <official_title>Four Cycles of R-CHOP Followed by Four Cycles of Rituximab Versus Six Cycles of R-CHOP Followed by Two Cycles of Rituximab in the Treatment of de Novo, Low-risk, Non-bulky Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma.</official_title>
